Welcome to the GEVS voting platform

GEVS (General Election Voting System) is an innovative native Android app developed for CO7102 Coursework 2, strategically crafted to address historical election issues in Shangri-La. Offering secure online voting, live tracking, post notifications, dark mode, analytics, and more, it stands as a robust solution for a transparent, inclusive, and technologically advanced democratic future.
